kingdom@kingdom-OptiPlex-390:~/Exts/stip-2.0-linux$ ./bin/stipshow --help

This program displays pre-detected space-time interest points
and optionally creates a video with s-t points overlayed on the
original video.

Usage:
   -v  filename : input video file name
   -f  filename : input STIP features file name
   -o  filename : output video file name (optional)
   -ff integer  : first frame (optional)
   -lf integer  : last frame (optional)
   -p           : pause after each frame

